Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------ANIME-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是小心点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画的是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.85,0:02:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是柠檬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是柠檬？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柠檬的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这样解释就行了吗  望月同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来这个柠檬就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不符合教学的主旨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以后这样的东西只限在美术部内部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样完成这幅画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢蒙克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}爱德华·蒙克：挪威画家，画风对德国表现主义起到了重要影响，代表作有《呐喊》等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望月同学和普通人画的都不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柠檬在呐喊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  在呐喊的是这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捂住耳朵是因为被呐喊声吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你是美术部的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年又开始社团活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同学不参加社团活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来美术部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敕使河原同学  你又在画什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果可没有手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来苹果就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我认真画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}回答「是」才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是一点兴趣也没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同学觉得三神老师怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么问我…不太好说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到蒙克的「呐喊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看的话不觉得很可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会感到不安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安吗…说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感到不安也是无可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能引出这种心境的画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为让你不安所以喜欢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算装作看不见也没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  榊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在讨论三神老师的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  我们在讨论更黑暗一点的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  黑暗的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于笼罩世界的不安感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敕使河原同学有感觉过不安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到升到三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却偏偏被分到这个被诅咒的三班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  榊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就想告诉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说下去就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  榊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个人没有阻止你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅画是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以谁为原型的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说是你想象的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者…都有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还要给她画上一对巨大的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在雨中做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不讨厌雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的是冬天冰冷的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种几乎快化作雪的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的左眼怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在医院见到的时候就一直戴着眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不想说的话不用勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该回去上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新面孔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是三年三班的榊原
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚转学过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是馆长千曳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来的话以后再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  现在快点离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千曳先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那个房间的主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有那种感觉呢  那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图书馆的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不亲切  总是穿着黑衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生一般都觉得他有点阴森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有对你说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二号图书室以前就在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过成为二号是应该在新校舍建成后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  恒一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打算参加社团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来今天被邀请要不要加入美术部了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢美术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不怎么擅长画画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此还…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我还没和别人说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  我想考一个美术系的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  这可是第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想试试雕刻和造型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有点不自量力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你父亲一定会反对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算你毕业了  也未必能找到相应的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也要看你的才能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕没有好运的话是没戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想的话就去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事在做之前就放弃的话就太逊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:10:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己看来是酷还是逊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉呢  白天太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗  在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  最近在读什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野小姐推荐给我的John  Saul的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs15}John Saul：美国悬疑恐怖小说作家，畅销代表作有《Suffer the Children》，《The Blackstone Chronicles》等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我这边的同事也去看看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你不是说这事来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事想要问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周一是不是有个女生在这医院去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周一？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你还在住院的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…只是有点在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来事出有因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我负责的病人里应该没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  还有另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天你有在医院里看到一个穿着校服的女生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是女生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深蓝色的上衣  短发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左眼还戴着眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼罩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眼科的病人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说去世的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说去世的是一个年轻的病人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮你查一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是随口问问的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问到什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用手机联系你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是我提出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作是同好的好意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你好像也有你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过下次要告诉我理由哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  恐怖少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如大家所知道的  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「俳句」是以「五七五」十七个音节构成的定型诗中的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「俳句」这个词也算是比较新的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约一百年前  被正冈子规所命名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前  人们称之为「徘谐」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成俳句有三个要点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我来一下    
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  你是在夜见山的医院出生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像马上就回东京了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后就一直在东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有回来探过亲吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲生下我后很快就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就没怎么回来过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要问这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得在哪里见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认错人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想确认的也包括那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不是说你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法清楚地想起来  自己不争气的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤泽同学  别想得太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是对策组成员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不好好做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策组成员是做什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说  为了保护同学而制定方案并予以执行的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护？制定方案和执行？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒一同学还没有搞清在三班所发生的事情  以及班上制定的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤泽同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只休息了一天就给我搞成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜见黄昏下  虚无苍之瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}请进吧  ——工房M
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原君？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你跟我说的事  已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是一名初中女生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母伤心欲绝  现场一片混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字呢  那女生叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太确定…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:17:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去世的人叫「Misaki」或是「Masaki」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…类似的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从别人那儿听到的  不知道是否准确…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  年轻的男生可不多见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是客人吗？还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…这里是店铺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是中学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  夜见北的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  收你半价就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是人偶店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有拿来卖的  不过可不是中学生能买得起的价位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢  请你好好观赏一番
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有其他客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要的话  还可以给你泡杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  不过茶就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请慢慢观赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}楼下展区由此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣…为什么会在这…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你不讨厌这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是为了吓你才躲起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是你碰巧来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得很像我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有一半
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还只是一半以下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我并不讨厌这里  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你又为什么  榊原同学又为什么在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个因为…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便走走…那个…还没有习惯小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就对偶然找到的这里产生了兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:22:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人觉得这里的人偶很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同学不这么认为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢的是她们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们显现出非常平静的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身体相连  还显得如此平静
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思议了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为身体相连才能如此平静…不是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是说身体互不相连而显得平静的话  还显得正常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看看吧…  这眼罩之下
